content:
I think there's been a misunderstanding. There's no such thing as "auto racking" or "Rack Wars" competition. It seems like you might have gotten your terminology mixed up.

Auto racing, track days, or motorcycle racing are common activities where riders or drivers compete on a track or course. However, "auto racking" doesn't seem to be a real thing.

If you're interested in improving your racing or riding skills, I'd be happy to provide tips and advice. But if you're looking for information on "auto racking," I'm afraid I won't be able to help you with that.
